PrecisApproval of the appointment by the Minister of Communications of Bertrand Morin, of Sherbrooke, Quebec, as a trustee of the Board of Trustees of the National Gallery of Canada to hold office during pleasure for a term of three years, in the place of Claudette Hould, whose term has expired.

precis:
Approval of the appointment by the Minister of Communications of
Bertrand Morin, of Sherbrooke, Quebec, as a trustee of the Board of
